    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older vehicle in fair overall condition and priced honestly at $16,900. It runs and drives, and it can serve well as practical transportation, but it clearly shows its age with cosmetic wear inside and out. Expect blemishes in the paint and trim, normal wear in the cabin, and the kind of minor aging issues you typically see on an older vehicle. This is not a showroom example, but for a buyer looking for a usable, straightforward vehicle at a reasonable price, it offers solid value.",
