    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation without the premium price tag. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who appreciates straightforward value, practical utility, and the opportunity to own at a very accessible price point. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive transportation with honest character, this one deserves a look.",
